{"tid":998602,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"羅致光宣布暫緩扣減200元安排　指觀察6個月再考慮","createTime":"2019-01-28T05:52:02.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-28T06:47:53.000Z","uid":75969,"like":0,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"54ce93062bad533666344da3f514b4db4bc6f8a3","tid":998602,"uid":75969,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-28T05:52:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20190128/s00001/b8f33feb9e008eec7f4cbd9135e06011.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20190128%2Fs00001%2Fb8f33feb9e008eec7f4cbd9135e06011.jpg&h=976070db&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n長者綜援年齡資格下月起由60歲上調至65歲，而60至64歲綜援健全受助人，若不參加自力更生綜合就業援助計劃覓工作，每月會扣減200元綜援金，新安排引起社福界反彈。勞工及福利局長羅致光今早在立法會福利事務委員會宣布暫緩扣減200元安排，直至其他措施檢討完成，及觀察未來6個月有關人士參與計劃情況，再決定是否恢復安排。<br />\n<br />\n羅致光會上指出，下月起新安排下，會要求60至64歲健全受助人每兩個月找兩份工、每兩個月見社工一次，若連續三次不符合相關要求，才會每月被扣減200元綜援金，換言之，最快今年8月後才會出現相關安排。不過他指，考慮到社會意見後，決定暫緩執行有關安排，直至完成綜援檢討，並會觀察首6個月相關人士參與計劃的情況，再考慮會否恢復安排。<br />\n<br />\n羅致光續說，政府將會檢討綜援不同項目包括補助金及特別津貼，計劃於今年內完成檢討。<br />\n<br />\n民建聯葛珮帆質疑，為何政府願意暫緩扣減200元綜援金安排，卻不願意擱置整個收緊長者綜援年齡資格安排，促請局方擱置政策，與民共議。公民黨郭家麒批評政府暫緩的安排是「言語藝術」，「一時一樣，無公信力」。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/ins/港聞/article/20190128/s00001/1548644531747/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E%2Farticle%2F20190128%2Fs00001%2F1548644531747%2F&d=%2B6PerixXDkZX5A3TLqthDkbWhtBCnEJYRTWbVbFBOac%3D&h=32d74afd\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E%2Farticle%2F20190128%2Fs00001%2F1548644531747%2F&h=ae9591c1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/ins/港聞/article/20190128/s00001/1548644531747/</a>"},{"pid":"60489fd962f75d72c126aed983ccedf88b849e26","tid":998602,"uid":35870,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-28T05:57:38.000Z","msg":"屌"},{"pid":"6101508655efca09e16fe508192665a9366b1726","tid":998602,"uid":4174,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-28T05:57:56.000Z","msg":"屌你老母 200蚊就斤斤計較<br />\n但d 工程 每日150 新移民福利就幾百幾千億咁送"},{"pid":"c9a382164506769d4b4b98b5f22b70222962fd3b","tid":998602,"uid":9838,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-28T06:03:44.000Z","msg":"無撚用，d廢老嘈兩句就退"},{"pid":"3b6436f8a5df2aa356ad4da4e9749afbf90129f6","tid":998602,"uid":46943,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-28T06:03:45.000Z","msg":"等水温熱先煮蛙<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b4d38d7ac1294f3b1131064d496bbe7de3aa5ab2","tid":998602,"uid":51701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6101508655efca09e16fe508192665a9366b1726","tid":998602,"uid":4174,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-28T05:57:56.000Z","msg":"屌你老母 200蚊就斤斤計較<br />\n但d 工程 每日150 新移民福利就幾百幾千億咁送"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-28T06:04:14.000Z","msg":"單程證洗一次腎都唔止條數啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1364678d1ff1e389d154af741c526f3033fc57e0","tid":998602,"uid":2736,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-28T06:04:55.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"642117b4779a5166b073c31279e690feb44ba84b","tid":998602,"uid":164387,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-28T06:05:34.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"5591457e9ab2adf656deca0b252398fc2030e594","tid":998602,"uid":60279,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-28T06:06:08.000Z","msg":"朝令夕改<br />\n無能到呢..."},{"pid":"bb964acc88413e46e815a38c0b3b50a6c0ee9c3e","tid":998602,"uid":55548,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-28T06:07:41.000Z","msg":"呢條正垃圾"},{"pid":"ecc3b2ecdfd7743ee57626d596c4da6354645039","tid":998602,"uid":162409,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-28T06:24:42.000Z","msg":"呢個咩自力更生計劃咪又係之前雜種up既要人民自力更生<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gi